description: Southern Routes has been feeding festival goers and party throwers their delicious comfort grub for over 4 years, and with their new truck, they can take their soulful creations straight to you.Their immensely mouthwatering menu includes Po’Boys with Andouille Sausage, Nashville Hot Chicken, Grilled Mahi Mahi, and Blackened Shrimp. You’ll also find delightfully delicious sides like Cajun Wedge Fries, Red Beans & Rice, Chicken Sausage Gumbo, and so much mo’!For some thoroughly wonderful cuisine, make your way out to Southern Routes.
name: Southern Routes Catering
